{"tid":1987541,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"澳洲促獨立調查疫情　中方斥政治操弄","createTime":"2020-04-24T13:58:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-24T14:47:21.000Z","uid":227801,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5d939a7cd310344d883d93c366ac94bb08f6af38","tid":1987541,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T13:58:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=388729&amp;fbclid=IwAR3YZHxP3xAnxaaKlLT1UXdkoZ7mmdsC776exZi2oubwUfGR04wu9mJ7Aso\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D388729%26fbclid%3DIwAR3YZHxP3xAnxaaKlLT1UXdkoZ7mmdsC776exZi2oubwUfGR04wu9mJ7Aso&d=6Js6kSUmrxq5WnxEZabkn8emYpZY8oJkMX6FO%2BQoeBQ%3D&h=5dd38085\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D388729%26fbclid%3DIwAR3YZHxP3xAnxaaKlLT1UXdkoZ7mmdsC776exZi2oubwUfGR04wu9mJ7Aso&h=99c72832\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=388729&amp;fbclid=IwAR3YZHxP3xAnxaaKlLT1UXdkoZ7mmdsC776exZi2oubwUfGR04wu9mJ7Aso</a><br />\n2020年4月23日 18:26<br />\n【Now新聞台】澳洲總理莫里森呼籲，世界衛生組織成員國應支持獨立調查新型冠狀病毒疫情，中方批評澳洲的提議是政治操弄。<br />\n<br />\n外交部發言人耿爽批評澳洲提議的所謂獨立調查，實際上是搞政治操弄，干擾國際疫情防控合作，不得人心，認為澳洲是出於政治目的，無端質疑及指摘極不負責任，奉勸對方放下意識形態偏見。<br />\n<br />\n耿爽又稱，中方早前已向世衛捐款二千萬美元，並會追加三千萬美元的現匯捐款，體現中國政府及人民對世衛的支持及信任。<br />\n<br />\n莫里森早前促請各國領袖支持調查病毒源頭及病毒如何擴散，指所有世衛成員國都有責任及義務參與這項調查，令世界變得更安全。"},{"pid":"4c04e4c49a375726849c833a264c53b6d176d516","tid":1987541,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T14:38:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abaf6dd6b6a4443c5ac9a31a7d6205e2dc5bca11","tid":1987541,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T14:43:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e53d513f3d08be6267c5bf48ea12e0497f4ed13","tid":1987541,"uid":225130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T14:44:37.000Z","msg":"蝗蟲真係世紀大賤種"},{"pid":"77deb12ed1bf12dc3609985113aaa45f10910d23","tid":1987541,"uid":19353,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-24T14:47:21.000Z","msg":"而家攞明係操弄你㗎啦 八國聯軍聽過未呀 中國歷史使唔使再教過你 唔係歷史中學習 就只會重演歷史"}]}